From: Sam Saffron <sam.saffron@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 22 Nov 2025 13:35:07 +1100
Subject: [PATCH] Feature: UI improvements to share picker

1. Default to windows tab (override with XDPH_PICKER_DEFAULT_TAB=screen)
2. Show preview of window when selecting windows
